{"tid":836794,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"上環商廈男子墮樓亡 妻子重傷不治","createTime":"2018-09-26T02:09:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-26T02:50:30.000Z","uid":41404,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"f2367b8f87e454fcd676a65ebfe0d85eb974aac0","tid":836794,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T02:09:56.000Z","msg":"早上7時54分，上環皇后大道中340號華秦國際大廈，一名男子由高處墮下，倒卧平台，經救護員檢驗證實當場死亡。與此同時，大廈保安員報案，指一名女子在單位內重傷昏迷，救護員將她送院，惟經搶救後證實不治。<br />\n<br />\n警方正調查兩人身份及事件原因，探員正翻查大廈閉路電視錄影，確定二人的出入時間；又借用平台一個寫字樓，查看死者的隨身物品。<br />\n<br />\n從閉路電視影像可見，男事主穿著藍色上衫、深色長褲，肩膊上有一個白色袋，清晨6時26分出現在大廈範圍，升降機閉路電視也拍攝到他上落。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180926/58723926\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180926%2F58723926&d=K%2BiddrwNjGpv%2BTt7PTNmecn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=04bf6fa5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180926%2F58723926&h=b5978d1a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180926/58723926</a>"},{"pid":"cb3ed4be815856345c61305f0e04cc8783dfc43d","tid":836794,"uid":54373,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T02:12:10.000Z","msg":"明明5毛話跳樓飛去對面馬路好正常<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d37cdbd25f01ff1650df85ebd3bd9459baa4f04","tid":836794,"uid":67500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T02:45:51.000Z","msg":"綠帽??"},{"pid":"5e3481926d19e7f4aa566f813b4a28dd0130f060","tid":836794,"uid":15813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T02:50:30.000Z","msg":"係我公司後面<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}